[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "錬金術部のみんなも快く協力してくれて\n助かったでござるな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01133",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "レスナちゃんたちに任せておけば安心だよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01134",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "まあ、腕は確かなようだしね。\nこの間のライブの時も……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01135",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "そういえば、あの時の礼もまだきちんとできていない\nというのに……また借りができてしまったな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01136",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "その借りは、本番で返すのがプロというものですわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01137",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "社長！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01138",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "この学園という舞台で、完璧なパフォーマンスを\n披露し、宴を大いに盛り上げる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01139",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "それこそがアイドルとして為すべき「礼」でしょう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01140",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "……御意",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01141",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "そういえば、結局本番には間に合いそうなわけ？\nそれがダメなら借りを返すとか以前の問題だけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01142",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "それは……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01143",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "そ、それは……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01144",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "無事、運営からも正式にゴーサインが出ましたわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01145",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "三人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おおっ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01146",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おおっ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01147",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おおっ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01148",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "人も、モノも、各所の協力のおかげで\nなんとか目途が立ちました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01149",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "学園の生徒たちはもちろん、\n『ＱＥジーンズ』の宣伝も効果てきめんでしたわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01150",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "それなら、あとは本番で結果を出すだけね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01151",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ちなみに、本番のタイムテーブルも確定しました。\nあなたたちの順番は……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01152",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "１番目。すなわちトップバッターですわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01153",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "嘘！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01154",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "公募枠の拙者たちが！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01155",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "会場を０から盛り上げなくてはなりませんから、\n若く勢いのあるグループが選ばれることが多いのです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_01156",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "ふん、上等じゃない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01157",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "盛り上げるための演出も考えなくてはならんな。\nレスナ殿にも相談に乗っていただこう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01158",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "うーん、ワクワクしてきた！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01159",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "うむ。我ら『Ｃｕｔｉｅ☆ＡｎｉｍａＬ』の晴れ舞台、\n必ずやみんなの期待に応えてみせようぞ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01160",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "三人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おー！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01161",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おー！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_01162",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おー！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_01163",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]